Making a release
----------------

1. Update version in setup.py and docs/conf.py (three places in total).
1. Update NEWS with changes, version number and date.
1. Commit all changes and tag (git tag -s -m 'tellcore-py version x.y.z')
1. Push new version to Python Package Index: ./setup.py sdist upload
1. Make new documenation version visible online:
   https://readthedocs.org/dashboard/tellcore-py/versions/
